IRC Server Propsal

For this project, our goal is to set up an IRC server and we were given the option to use a raspberry pi. There werenâ€™t many rules leaving the project for us to come up with an idea and run with it.

Objectives:
  ~First I needed to understand what an IRC Server was and what it did.
  ~Second I would need to know how to set up a Raspberry Pi.
  ~Third learn how to burn an ISO file to a SD card
  ~Fourth I need to find the software needed to do this
