I think this project will be interesting for the fact that I will be learning more about linux, how to set up and use a raspberry pi and also to finally understand more about IRC in general. After a quick cursery search i found a few resources that will help out alot. Between Wikipedia, pimylifeup.com and raspberrypi.org I should be able to accomplish this fairly well.


